  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the prevalence of Fabry mutations in patients with
      left ventricular hypertrophy (moderate to severe), as measured by echocardiography.This study
      is a screening study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
