  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Determination of the prevalence of Fabry mutations in patients with left ventricular hypertrophy (moderate to severe), as measured by echocardiography</measure>
    <time_frame>At baseline T0</time_frame>
    <description>patients with left ventricular hypertrophy will be screened for Fabry mutations, and results will be communicated within four months</description>
  </primary_outcome>
